TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: ng dng m hnh hc my trong d on p ng thuc
Tc gi lun vn: Nguyn Xun Tng Kha: 2018A
Ngi hng dn: TS. Ban H Bng
T kha (Keyword): Tin sinh hc, machine learning, deep learning
Ni dung tm tt:
a) L do chn ti
Hin nay, mt trong nhng mc tiu quan trng ca y hc c nhn ha l cung cp
phng php iu tr ph hp cho tng bnh nhn da trn c im sinh hc ca h. C mt
s d n ln trn th gii c trin khai nh GDSC, CCLE to ra mt lng ln d liu
sinh hc ca ngi bnh (-omics data) v d liu p ng thuc (drug response) cho cc dng
t bo (cell lines mang tt c cc c tnh sinh hc ca bnh nhn). Cc d n ny cung cp
ngun d liu phong ph v hu ch nh d liu sinh hc biu hin gene (gene expression,)
d liu t bin gene (mutation), d liu v p ng thuc vi cc dng t bo bnh khc
nhau, to iu kin thun li cho cc nghin cu tin lm sng n cc th nghim lm
sng trn ngi. Tuy nhin cc ngun d liu ny cha y v cn mt lng ln cc loi
thuc v cc dng t bo cha c tnh ton, th nghim. Ngoi ra, s a dng, phc tp,
khng ng nht gia cc yu t gy bnh, gia cc ngi bnh khc nhau, hay c ch sinh
hc gia cc gen, gia cc bnh, gia cc thuc cng nh gia cc cp quan h ny ngy cng
tr nn phong ph to nn nhng thch thc khng nh cho vic tnh ton d on d liu
lm sng. Bn cnh , s pht trin nhanh chng ca cng ngh thng tin v cc phng
php tnh ton, x l d liu ln gn y to iu kin thc y vic pht trin cc phng
php d on p ng thuc nhm h tr cc bc s c thm thng tin trong qu trnh iu tr.
c th nng cao nhng hiu bit v ng dng cc phng php tnh ton trong khoa
hc my tnh hin nay vo lnh vc d on p ng thuc. Ti quyt nh thc hin ti
ng dng m hnh hc my trong d on p ng thuc cho lun vn ny.
b) Mc ch, i tng, phm vi nghin cu
- Nghin cu v cc d liu y sinh hc lin quan n p ng thuc.
- Nghin cu cc phng php tnh ton d on p ng thuc.
- p dng mt s m hnh tnh ton hin nay cho bi ton d on p ng thuc.
c) Phng php nghin cu
- Nghin cu l thuyt:
o Nghin cu, phn tch d liu y sinh hc lin quan n p ng thuc trn cc
dng t bo
- Nghin cu cc ti liu lin quan n hc my, hc c gim st, phn lp d liu, rng
ngu nhin, my vector h tr; phng php hc su.
2
- Nghin cu thc nghim:
o La chn tp d liu thc nghim
o ng dng cc k thut hc my: Random forest, Support Vector Machine,
Deep Learning trn b d liu thc nghim, so snh hiu nng cc phng
php ny
d) B cc ca lun vn
Lun vn gm 4 chng chnh:
1. Chng 1: Trnh by tng quan c s l thuyt v hc my v vic ng dng hc my
trong d on p ng thuc
2. Chng 2: M t bi ton v trnh by phng php gii quyt bi ton
3. Chng 3: Ci t th nghim v nh gi
4. Kt lun v hng pht trin
